abstract: Denmark's national soccer team wins spot in 2012 European Championships.
snippet: Denmark won a spot in the 2012 European Championships at the expense of Portugal, and France needed a late penalty kick in a 1-1 tie with Bosnia-Herzegovina to qualify.
lead_paragraph: Denmark won a spot in the 2012 European Championships at the expense of Portugal, and France needed a late penalty kick in a 1-1 tie with Bosnia-Herzegovina to qualify.

headline.seo: Denmark Beats Portugal to Make European Championships
